wiki.content: The She's Thunderstorms Songfacts reports that Alex Turner penned this in the New York apartment he shared at the time with his girlfriend, Alexa Chung, during a "mad" thunderstorm. wiki.summary: The She's Thunderstorms Songfacts reports that Alex Turner penned this in the New York apartment he shared at the time with his girlfriend, Alexa Chung, during a "mad" thunderstorm.
